Conexant Agrees to Be Acquired by Golden Gate Capital, Ending SMSC Accord

-- B y   S t e f a n i e   B a t c h o - L i n o
-- 
2011-02-23T21:32:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/conexant-agrees-to-be-acquired-by-golden-gate-capital-ending-smsc-accord.html
  Conexant Systems Inc . said it signed
a definitive merger agreement with Gold Holdings Inc., under
which Gold Holdings will purchase all of the outstanding shares
of Conexant common stock at a price of $2.40 per share in cash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
